holding the rope.

689
00:44:59,833 --> 00:45:00,833
<font color="#E69138"><b>TOKYO</b></font>: Yeah.

690
00:45:13,166 --> 00:45:15,833
<font color="#E69138"><b>TOKYO</b></font>: <font color="#00FF7F"><i>We know
nothing can go wrong when you're here.</i></font>

691
00:45:23,083 --> 00:45:24,833
You'll pull an ace from your sleeve.

692
00:45:24,916 --> 00:45:27,166
<font color="#87CEFA">(protesters clamoring)</font>

693
00:45:33,541 --> 00:45:35,416
You're the master of illusion.

694
00:45:42,625 --> 00:45:44,625
That's why we go back into the lion's den.

695
00:45:50,416 --> 00:45:52,500
<font color="#00FF7F"><i>Even if they point a thousand guns at us.</i></font>

696
00:45:57,375 --> 00:45:59,000
Because we all believe in you.

697
00:46:01,166 --> 00:46:02,166
Like a mantra.

698
00:46:03,333 --> 00:46:05,708
<font color="#87CEFA">(crowd chanting)</font> Professor! Professor!

699
00:46:15,583 --> 00:46:16,666
You're our faith.

