00:46:17,333 --> 00:46:19,333
<font color="#87CEFA">(crowd cheering)</font>

701
00:46:20,166 --> 00:46:22,458
<font color="#E69138"><b>TOKYO</b></font>: <font color="#00FF7F"><i>The faith that, if all else fails,</i></font>

702
00:46:24,333 --> 00:46:25,583
